---
// Our Philosophy - Foundation Charter Page
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Foundation Charter - Storysmith">

<!-- [PHILOSOPHY HERO] -->
<section class="bg-brand-navy text-white py-32 md:py-40 relative overflow-hidden">
    
    <!-- Optional: Very subtle large text watermark for texture -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[20rem] font-serif text-white/[0.03] pointer-events-none whitespace-nowrap select-none">
        Mana
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center relative z-10">
        
        <span class="text-brand-peach font-sans uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm font-bold mb-6 block">
            Our Foundation Charter
        </span>

        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 leading-tight">
            Our Covenant with You,<br /> 
            Your Family, and the <span class="italic text-brand-peach">Seven Generations</span> to Come.
        </h1>

        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-brand-peach mx-auto mb-12"></div>

        <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl italic leading-loose text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            "This is not a marketing document. This is the source code for our integrity."
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

  <!-- Section 2: E Ku Tikanga, E Ku Mana -->
  <section class="bg-brand-white text-brand-black py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-6">
        E aku tikanga, e aku mana
      </h2>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl text-center mb-12 text-brand-black/70">
        To my principles, to my authority
      </h3>
      <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-loose text-center">
        I, the founder, stand as Tangata Moana—Samoan and New Zealand European—carrying the wisdom of both worlds. My work honours my tūpuna (ancestors), serves my whānau (family), and considers the mokopuna (descendants) seven generations ahead. Storysmith is built from this place of mana (dignity) and hau (life force), ensuring that what we create enhances the collective.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Our Three Core Values -->
  <section class="bg-brand-white text-brand-black py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">

      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-20">
        Our Foundation: Three Core Values
      </h2>

      <div class="mb-20">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">1. Dignity in the Design (Vā - The Sacred Space)</h3>
        <blockquote class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl italic border-l-4 border-brand-navy pl-6 mb-6 text-brand-black/80">"We tend the sacred space where trust and insight can flourish."</blockquote>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-loose">A story is a space of vulnerability and connection. We are the guardians of that space, ensuring every interaction is designed to protect the mana (dignity) of the storyteller. Your trust is our most precious currency.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-20">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">2. Empowerment in the Process (Utu Tūturu - Reciprocity)</h3>
        <blockquote class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl italic border-l-4 border-brand-navy pl-6 mb-6 text-brand-black/80">"We build to give back more than we take."</blockquote>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-loose">Our technology exists to empower, not to extract. We measure our success by the capability we build in others. This is a partnership where your investment of time and vulnerability is met with our deepest commitment to honouring your story.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">3. Sovereignty in the Story (Mana Motuhake - Your Data)</h3>
        <blockquote class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl italic border-l-4 border-brand-navy pl-6 mb-6 text-brand-black/80">"Your story is yours. Completely. Forever."</blockquote>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-loose">The data generated in a conversation is a sacred story belonging to you. You are the sole owner. You have the right to delete your data at any time, permanently and without question. Your stories will never be sold, shared, or used for AI training. Ever.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Our Sacred Boundaries -->
  <section class="bg-gray-100 text-brand-black py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">

      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-20">
        Our Sacred Boundaries
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16">

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8">What We NEVER Do:</h3>
          <ul class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-loose space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">❌</span><span>Sell or share your personal stories.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">❌</span><span>Use your data for AI training.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">❌</span><span>Create "AI clones" or simulate a person after they're gone.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">❌</span><span>Build solutions that exploit vulnerability or create dependency.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">❌</span><span>Prioritise profit over the wellbeing and dignity of people.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8">What We ALWAYS Do:</h3>
          <ul class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-loose space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">✅</span><span>Start with empathy and deep listening.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">✅</span><span>Protect your privacy and sovereignty as fundamental rights.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">✅</span><span>Honour cultural protocols and dignity in every interaction.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">✅</span><span>Build for seven generations, not two quarters.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mr-3 shrink-0">✅</span><span>Build relationships based on trust, reciprocity, and transparency.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Final Promise -->
  <section class="bg-brand-navy text-brand-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
        Our Promise
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl leading-loose mb-12">
        "We promise to tend the vā (the sacred space), maintain utu tūturu (reciprocity), and uphold mana motuhake (your sovereignty). This is our covenant with you, your communities, and the seven generations to come."
      </p>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl italic mb-4">
        He waka eke noa
      </h3>
      <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl italic text-brand-white/90">
        (We are all in this canoe together)
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>